#Preprocess rds.list <- list() for(i in c(1:length(samples))){ #Load data sp <- samples[[i]] mtx_path <- data[[i]] sc_counts <- Read10X(mtx_path) sce <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = sc_counts, assay = "RNA",min.cells = 0, min.features = 0, project = sp) #Add meta information sce@meta.data$Age <- Ages[[i]] sce@meta.data$BioSample <- BioSample[[i]] #Calculate MT percent sce[["percent.mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(sce, pattern = "^MT-") #Quality control sce <- subset(sce,subset = nCount_RNA < 10000 & nCount_RNA > 200 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nFeature_RNA < 2500 & percent.mt < 10) #Normalize and calculate cell cycele score sce <- NormalizeData(sce) sce <- FindVariableFeatures(sce, selection.method = "vst") sce <- CellCycleScoring(sce, s.features = cc.genes$s.genes, g2m.features = cc.genes$g2m.genes, set.ident = TRUE) print(BioSample[[i]]) print(sce) rds.list <- append(rds.list,sce) } #Merge data in Seurat v5 hro_rna <- merge(rds.list[[1]],rds.list[-1]) hro_rna[["RNA"]] <- JoinLayers(hro_rna[["RNA"]])
